p>I&#8217;d never really thought much about snails, but I loved these images. Something in them spoke to me. I downloaded a bunch and stitched them together and printed them out to serve as <a href="https://austinkleon.com/tag/guardian-spirits/">guardian spirits</a> for my new diary. </p><p>At first I liked the idea of &#8220;fighting off the snail,&#8221; like the snail was sloth, or sluggishness, something to be slain or run through. I drew myself in the place of the knights in my diary: </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98885e24-a168-4883-83d9-728f9cd08f9e.heic" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98885e24-a168-4883-83d9-728f9cd08f9e.heic 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98885e24-a168-4883-83d9-728f9cd08f9e.heic 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98885e24-a168-4883-83d9-728f9cd08f9e.heic 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98885e24-a168-4883-83d9-728f9cd08f9e.heic 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98885e24-a168-4883-83d9-728f9cd08f9e.heic" width="1024" height="1024" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/98885e24-a168-4883-83d9-728f9cd08f9e.heic&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1024,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:305381,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/heic&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98885e24-a168-4883-83d9-728f9cd08f9e.heic 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98885e24-a168-4883-83d9-728f9cd08f9e.heic 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98885e24-a168-4883-83d9-728f9cd08f9e.heic 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98885e24-a168-4883-83d9-728f9cd08f9e.heic 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Not sure what possessed me to write &#8220;<a href="https://austinkleon.com/2017/07/06/silence-is-a-space-for-something-new-to-happen/#:~:text=The%20Quakers%3A%20&#8220;Do%20not%20speak,distracted%20to%20probably%20ultimately%20survive.">Silence is a space for something to happen</a>&#8221; in the middle of the page, but it later became significant when I learned that snails don&#8217;t have ears!</figcaption></figure></div><p>Then last Tuesday I was dropping my kids off at school after a big rain and I <em>saw </em>a real live snail on the sidewalk. (It rained for several days straight in Texas last week.) This snail didn&#8217;t look like any kind of threat to anything. It looked downright friendly, in fact. </p><p>Something I learned a long time ago is that it is a great help to the artist to believe that <em>there are no coincidences</em>. One way to boost your curiosity is to just assume that everything in life is a clue left from the universe for further investigation. Follow the clues the universe drops for you, and you will almost always learn something interesting. Take everything as a sign and you&#8217;ll be less stumped about what to do next. </p><p>I decided to start reading about snails. My first research stop is usually the <a href="https://austinkleon.com/2019/04/29/the-childrens-section/">children&#8217;s section</a>, but my kids only had one book on their shelves called <em><a href="https://geni.us/FRS0">The Slug</a></em>. So I downloaded David George Gordon&#8217;s <em><a href="https://www.publishersweekly.com/9781570616112">The Secret World of Slugs and Snails: Life in the Very Slow Lane</a> </em>and spent the morning learning about the invertebrates. </p><p>Fascinating creatures! Given that they can &#8220;sleep for hours, days, weeks, and months,&#8221; they seemed to me good mascots for the winter. (Though it should be pointed out that they are also excellent at <a href="https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/estivate">estivating</a> in the summer!) I started doodling them in my diary.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a5c10e3-a10b-4b21-b674-7533789c0b0e_1179x2096.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a5c10e3-a10b-4b21-b674-7533789c0b0e_1179x2096.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a5c10e3-a10b-4b21-b674-7533789c0b0e_1179x2096.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a5c10e3-a10b-4b21-b674-7533789c0b0e_1179x2096.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a5c10e3-a10b-4b21-b674-7533789c0b0e_1179x2096.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a5c10e3-a10b-4b21-b674-7533789c0b0e_1179x2096.jpeg" width="398" height="707.5555555555555" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0a5c10e3-a10b-4b21-b674-7533789c0b0e_1179x2096.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:2096,&quot;width&quot;:1179,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:398,&quot;bytes&quot;:827340,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quo